television news in Atlanta.
   A motion by Lowe's attorneys denies he ``has committed any
wrongful acts giving rise to liability.'' But a motion from Ms.
Wilson's attorney says witnesses have confirmed Lowe had sex with
Miss Parsons, and contends that Lowe has admitted it to his
California lawyers.
   Lowe's attorneys have contended that Ms. Wilson and her former
husband attempted to blackmail the actor before filing their
lawsuit, but Ms. Wilson's attorney denies any such attempt.
